ackground-color: #ccc;">  collapse of an algorithmic stablecoin</a> is one =
of the least surprising events in the world, right up there with =E2=80=9Ca=
 crypto exchange steals or loses its customers=E2=80=99 money.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">This is the problem with my rough model of the=
 crypto credit crisis of 2022. It=E2=80=99s easy for me now to say =E2=80=
