<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The basic situation is that Elon Musk is more =
or less the richest person in the world, and he owns Twitter, and Twitter d=
oes not seem to be <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click=
/29960075.267530/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9hcnRpY2xlcy90d2l0dGVycy1hZHZlcn=
