<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The way that the modern US economy works is th=
at if you want to buy a car from me, and I want to sell you the car, then y=
ou have to give me money, and I have to give you the car, and also we have =
to do a mysterious third thing in which we perform a magic ritual to coax m=
y spirit to depart=C2=A0from the car so that your spirit may enter it. That=
